{"title":"品格","authors":["殷增涛"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":7,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"品格"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殷增涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个黑色的幽灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潜入我们的城市；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场突发的灾难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在八百三十万人中降临；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场特殊的战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在没有硝烟中爆发；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个未曾耳闻的单词，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即刻家喻户晓，搅乱了安宁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"SARS，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在测试我们的城市；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非典，让我们同仇敌忾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如“九八”抗洪的命令！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的利益高于一切；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的生命重于泰山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让口罩不遮挡百姓的笑靥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让生命不受变异病毒的威胁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让发展的车轮不被瘟神入侵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲上去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们勇往直前，义无反顾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们曾经有过恐惧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪过彷徨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民需要是我们的天职，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战斗中冲锋是我们的使命；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沧海横流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更显英雄本色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"危难之中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更闪烁着党性光彩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚守，是我们的意志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奉献，是我们的境界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为民，是我们的宗旨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利，是我们的信念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血与火的抗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生与死的洗礼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱与情的凝聚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民和城市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锻造出非凡的品格，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谱写了生命的新歌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临危不惧、沉着应对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实事求是、尊重科学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舍生忘死、勇往直前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众一心、众志成城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结互助、敢于胜利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这辉映日月的品格，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这引人豪迈的新歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将载入历史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催人奋进。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}